name: System Overload (Taylor Made)
description:
Best played with fullscreen.

Your the only thing between the system and utter chaos. Your working as a security specialist it's your job to prevent the system from overloading. 

Simply type what you see to fix the system but watch out for the various types of incoming hacks...
